# Keep intake inbox templates/protocols tracked, but ignore per-thread exports.
intake/threads_inbox_*/**
!intake/threads_inbox_*/
!intake/threads_inbox_*/README.md
!intake/threads_inbox_*/PROTOCOL.md
!intake/threads_inbox_*/THREAD_PROMPT_github.md
